 it would be stupid. I will check tonight tho when I log on and find out. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukellaen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kellaen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/3/02 1:53:34 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4616.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: avalanche ale</span><hr size=1> LORE NODROP - that is all<br><br>Baradain and his goon bodyguards (3) are all dubious. He is light blue to a 60, the bodyguards are blue. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uprodigious.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Prodigious</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/3/02 5:15:43 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4616.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: avalanche ale</span><hr size=1> confirming magic lore no drop, not no rent.<br><br>btw the assist on these guys is screwy. i'm lvl 60 and when i've been doing it with the guy needing the brew on occasions, i pull from max range with mrylokar gaunts. sometimes i get one, but once i got 4 bodyguards and had to tank it all while killing berradain. i had another lvl 60 rogue with good gear there with me so it was np, but if you're lower level you might wanna bring either:<br><br>* druid/ranger for harmony<br>* FD class for pulling (captain doesn't move after being pulled, but bodyguards walk back)<br>* enough melee to tank adds while you kill berradain, and then run to the zone<br><br>make sure you have jboots, run3, sow or some form of run buff. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usaleani.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Saleani</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/3/02 1:28:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4616.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: avalanche ale</span><hr size=1> I make the stuff for MQ. It is no-drop. Definately NOT no-rent, since I usually have one on me ready to go.<br><br>You definately want an FD puller to get the guards split. Or, if you have a very well equipped lvl 60 bard, have him kite all the guards untill done (that was the wierdest MQ I was ever involved with).<br><br>Atone and mem-blur work to clear aggro on extras pulled, may need to cast it a few times. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=vaelin>Vaelin</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/4/02 1:40:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4616.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: avalanche ale</span><hr size=1> the ale was no rent for 2 or 3 weeks after this quest comes life but they changed it. meanwhile i did this part 5 times and harmony works good <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ubarazonvaz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>BarazonVaz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/4/02 4:14:45 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4616.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: avalanche ale</span><hr size=1> Thanks everyone for the replies.  Made one, succeeded on third try with 200 brewing and brewing contraption.<br><br>Another question, to clarify the guard pulling: do you mean to split the guards and kill them all before turning in the ale? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uaragain.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aragain</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/4/02 6:09:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4616.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: avalanche ale</span><hr size=1> Well, I think the best way to do it without problems is next :<br><br>1.) Harmony at 4 bodyguards, Ranger or Druid can do it.<br>2.) Give Tainted Avalanche Ale at Captain Berradin<br>3.) wait until Captain Berradin starts to move his arms, it is the moment when poison effects start on him.<br>4.) Captain Berradin despawn and spawn on Poisoned form fell on floor.<br>5.) Pull Captain Berradin now and Harmony again if it is needed.<br> <br>NOTE: Take care because Capatain Berradin on Poisoned form has a time to despawn, because his life down fastly for poison, Pull at him before he despawn or you lost Tainted Avalanche Ale. I think this time is 1 minute.<br><br>Time to spawn of Guards is really fast like 5 minutes no more. I think option to kill them before you do quest is difficult because they could respawn fastly. <br><br>I hope it help at you  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uaragain.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aragain</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/4/02 6:10:41 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4616.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: avalanche ale</span><hr size=1> Well, I think the best way to do it without problems is next :<br><br>1.) Give Tainted Avalanche Ale at Captain Berradin.<br>2.) Harmony at 4 bodyguards, Ranger or Druid can do it.<br>3.) Wait until Captain Berradin starts to move his arms, it is the moment when poison effects start on him.<br>4.) Captain Berradin despawn and spawn on Poisoned form fell on floor.<br>5.) Pull Captain Berradin now and Harmony again if it is needed.<br> <br>NOTE: Take care because Captain Berradin on Poisoned form has a time to despawn, because his life down fastly for poison, Pull at him before he despawn or you lost Tainted Avalanche Ale. I think this time is 1 minute.<br><br>Time to spawn of Guards is really fast like 5 minutes no more. I think option to kill them before you do quest is difficult because they could respawn fastly. <br><br>I hope it help at you  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uvaslin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vaslin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Head Safehouse Admin</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/4/02 8:47:28 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4616.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: avalanche ale</span><hr size=1> Ah, just do it my MQ way.  2 people max.<br><br>1) Put the person who receives the head/note in the room.<br>2) I hand in the brew<br>3) Aggro everyone.<br>4) Run like heck in big circles.<br>5) The person who is still in the room will kill the new Berradin when he respawns in the tent alone.<br>6) I zone when I see the loot message. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/utibishatter.showPublicProfile?language=EN>TibisHatter</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.top-hat.demon.co.uk/Images/10x10.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/4/02 9:29:13 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4616.topic&index=10>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: avalanche ale</span><hr size=1> Yep, worked a treat last night for us! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/utalis4u.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Talis4u</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/4/02 12:01:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4616.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: avalanche ale</span><hr size=1> ...<br><br>If you don't have harmony, anyone could just agro the bodyguards from range as long as Berradin is light blue.  Take them to a zone while the ale gets handed in/Berradin gets killed.<br><br>Or if you're super cool like the first person who did this, you could assassinate Berradin.. :P <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showPrevMessage?topicID=4616.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showNextMessage?topicID=4616.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4616.topic&index=11><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.emailToFriend?topicID=4616.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.threadControl?topicID=4616.topic><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/dagger.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4616.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4616.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion">Main Lounge<option value="thesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc">News Bulletin<option value="thesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies">Training Studio<option value="thesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers">The Back A